<plot>Miriam has just set the table for a romantic dinner for her friend, who is bringing the last chapters of his book over for her to edit. The book he is writing is a love story in which the protagonist may be hiding his true feelings for his muse. Miriam takes the hint and decides to help her shy would be novelist expose his true feelings for her. However, she is not expecting to hear what he has to say.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?366518</url></doc>
